comment: Winslow (MIA) maintains legal guarding position and Deng (MIA) cleanly blocks Nowitzki's (DAL) shot attempt. Any contact that occurred after the block is considered incidental.
Nowitzki (DAL) is in the paint without actively guarding an opponent for longer than three seconds.
Felton (DAL) clamps Wade's (MIA) arm, affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
As Bosh (MIA) hedges on the screen, he trips Felton (DAL) causing him to fall to the floor.
Bosh (MIA) sets the screen on Barea (DAL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
[Observable in enhanced video] Barea (DAL) moves his pivot foot prior to releasing his dribble.
Pachulia (DAL) and Deng (MIA) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Nowitzki (DAL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Winslow's (MIA) baseline drive.
Parsons (DAL) commits a take foul on Wade (MIA).
Bosh (MIA) legally contests Felton's (DAL) jump shot attempt.
